imdb.plot outline: A South Korea Variety Show. It consists of a permanent cast of eight 'Family' members, with one or more guests per episode. The cast visit various South Korean locations, residing overnight at an elderly couple home, while competing in games, preparing meals, and performing assigned house chores.
